nodes.text: Reeka was a female pilot who was the second-in-command of the Rebel Alliance squadron of Nath Tensent. Reeka had a face full of scars and at one point, threatened to disassemble Tensent's droid, T5. Along with the rest of Tensent's squadron, Reeka was killed by the forces of the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing during an attack on the Galactic Empire's Trenchenovu shipyards.
